<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 10px 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .status {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .status-label {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .meeting-info {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .meeting-info td, .meeting-info th {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 8px;
    }
    .meeting-info tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
    .meeting-info tr:hover {
      background-color: #ddd;
    }
    .meeting-info th {
      padding-top: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: left;
      background-color: #8254F8;
      color: white;
      min-width: 40%;
    }
    td {
      max-width: 60%;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .participant-organizer {
      color: #8254F8;
    }
    .participant-creator {
      color: blue;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #8254F8;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .banner {
        height: 50px;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #8254F8;
        text-align: center;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 40px;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .bravo-banner {
        margin: 20px auto;
        color: #8254F8;
        text-align: center;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .bravo-image {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }
    .item {
      border: 1px solid #8254F8;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color: #8254F8;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      width: fit-content;
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='container' style="background: white">
        <section class="banner">
            <img src='https://discoursefy-public-bucket.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Logo.jpg' alt="Discoursefy Logo" /> <span> Discoursefy.</span>
        </section>
        <section class="bravo-banner">
            <img src='https://discoursefy-public-bucket.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/bravoBanner.jpg' alt="Bravo Banner" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto; height: 180px" />
        </section>
        <div class='wrapper'>
            <h2>Congratulations! You've Been Selected as a {{category}} Category Creator</h2>
            <p>{{name}}, we are thrilled to inform you that you have successfully passed your screenings and have been selected as a {{category}} category creator.</p>
            <p>As a {{category}} creator, you can now set your meeting rate, sync your Google Calendar, and connect your Stripe account for seamless payment retrievals.</p>
            <div>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Take Me to My Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further information, please do not hesitate to reach out.</p>
            <p>
                Best regards,<br>
                Discoursefy.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
